    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >香肠大乱斗！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/ab0f8f04e96833debd6e1cd1b50084b4.poster.avif?t=1754320891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/ab0f8f04e96833debd6e1cd1b50084b4.webm?t=1754320891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/ab0f8f04e96833debd6e1cd1b50084b4.mp4?t=1754320891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>别掉以轻心！这是一个肠吃肠的世界。为了生存，你需要战斗到死，把你的敌人推向深渊，迸出番茄酱血汁！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和你的朋友大战一场！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/8ebe70784f3e2a8dc7991e88082000a0.poster.avif?t=1754320891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/8ebe70784f3e2a8dc7991e88082000a0.webm?t=1754320891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290210/extras/8ebe70784f3e2a8dc7991e88082000a0.mp4?t=1754320891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在残酷的香肠大战中，你需要疯狂甩头，推动敌对香肠撞向致命障碍，比如锋利的工具、厨房水槽、花园火焰…… 或者将它们推出台面，送它们赴死。城市太拥挤了，是时候清理下了！ 努力将所有香肠都推出去，将它们碎成渣渣！<br><br>在每场酣战结束后，别忘了跳一段香肠胜利之舞！ 成为小镇上最大的赢家！",
